-- Patria May Give Up Vulcabras Deal on Global Crisis, Estado Says
-- B y   T e l m a   M a r o t t o
-- 2012-06-30T13:38:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-30/patria-may-give-up-vulcabras-deal-on-global-crisis-estado-says.html
Patria Investimentos SA may give up
its plan to buy a stake in Brazilian shoemaker Vulcabras Azaleia
SA as private equity investors are becoming more cautious
because of the global financial crisis, O Estado de S. Paulo
reported, without saying where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Telma Marotto in  Sao Paulo  at 
 tmarotto1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Helder Marinho at 
 hmarinho@bloomberg.net . 